Hong Kong's return to China is a historic event not only to
China but also to the whole world. It is a great victory of the
Chinese people over colonialism, he added.
</P>
<P>
Nguyen Quang Khai, Vietnamese ambassador to Baghdad, said that
"Hong Kong's peaceful return to China sets a good example to the
world in such aspect."
</P>
<P>
He believed that the return, due on July 1, will have a
positive effect on the trade ties between Hong Kong and
Vietnam. 
</P>
