domestic and international markets, according to the experts.
</P>
<P>
They pointed out that technological and marketing cooperation
between Hong Kong and the inland areas will help increase their
competitiveness in hi-tech development in international market.
</P>
<P>
The seminar was sponsored by the related departments of the
Academy of Social Sciences of China.  
