with visiting Russian First Deputy Prime Minister Boris Yefimovich
Nemtsov.
</P>
<P>
-- US President Bill Clinton on Tuesday praised the House of
Representatives for backing his decision to extend the Most
Favored Nation trade status for China.  
</P>
